                    <span>This is alphabetically arrangement of unrelated concepts that only have in common that theyre are linked to JavaScript.<P>This is pretty much useless if you are looking for an anwer to a meaningful question. It is only useful in the case where you know the class/method and are looking for the table "which browser does it support it".<P>I definitely do not recommend it.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">The CD-ROM is handy</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>3</span>
